	"description": "CSS selectors are one of the most important parts of CSS. They give you the\nability to target HTML elements on your web page that you want to style.\n\nWithout CSS selectors, you wouldn&#x27;t be able to style your page to look how you\nwant.\n\nThankfully CSS selectors have been around for a while, and you can style\nelements on your page however you want. \n\nBut if you really want to unlock the power of CSS and create amazing elements,\nthen you need to understand what you can do with CSS selectors. Namely",
